datafield.subfield: By the author of 'Véra,' and 'The hôtel du petit St. Jean.'
The Hôtel du Petit St. Jean.
The literary remains of Albrecht Dürer.
Apparently an offprint; with a special lithographed t.p.; originally published in the Edinburgh review, July 1861.
Gift of Lessing J. Rosenwald, 1943-1975. Has bookplate of Howard C. Levis.
Lessing J. Rosenwald Reference Collection (Library of Congress)
The Maritime Alps and their seaboard,
ix, 395 p., [1] leaf of plates : ill. ; 19 cm.
Microfilm. Washington, D.C. : Library of Congress Photoduplication Service, 1986. 1 microfilm reel ; 35 mm.
